realisable value of assets being acquired amounted to Pounds 1m.
Consideration is payable as to Pounds 200,000 on completion with the balance
deferred until April 2.
In addition Drummond has an option, exercisable before the end of October,
to acquire the premises of the business at a price of Pounds 600,000 until
end-June and at market value thereafter.
