FT  02 JAN 92 / UK Company News: Celebrations for Tottenham Hotspur
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Tottenham Hotspur, owner of the north London football club, has room to
celebrate. Mr Gary Lineker, Spurs' star striker, was awarded an OBE in the
New Year's honours list and yesterday the club clinched a 2-1 victory over
